<br>
Break AT 2:00PM.  Please try to be there on time.  We will be clearing the east side of the zone primarily, where the arms, legs, and breastplates/robes drop.  Last time we had a few items rot, so let's stick to stuff that is tougher, but we know people can use.  We will most likely have a click stick cleric available, a level 60 tank, and some enchanters.  I think we have what it takes to clear the east half of the zone of normal creatures, and maybe even take down one of the named treants, Fayl by name.<br>
<br>
I'll post full loot rules (which I posted in an earlier thread) on the everquestraids link that I'd truly appreciate everyone interested signing up for.  This raid is open up to the Alliance, as well as Dragonkin.  Anyone else interested in attending please send me an email at dougjs@ameritech.net, or send me a tell ingame.  Recruits for invited guilds are welcome with prior request sent to me.<br>
<br>
I'm sticking a level limit of 50, as the creatures on the east side are significantly higher level than the west side, many types of them range in level from 55-60.  These are the normal mobs, not the named ones.  If you're below 50, you'll feel useless unless you're a buffing class.  Level 46-50 clerics I will make an exception for, as we know you'll be useful... just send me an email or a tell.<br>
<br>
Hope to see many of you there.  Let's see some new breastplates and robes!  And gems... TONS of gems!<br>
